<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <%= render partial: "shared/top_banner", locals: {title: "#{@community.name}"} %>
  </div>
  <div class="row profile">
    <section class="col-xs-3">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
          <%= image_tag "placeholder.jpg", class:"image" %>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12">
          <h2>Our Community</h2>
          <p>
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Hic aperiam quos iusto, dolorum aspernatur deleniti iste tenetur eligendi, minus dolore officia iure cupiditate quidem nobis quaerat veniam. Quo, officiis, facilis.
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Nesciunt nam quos officiis laborum sit perspiciatis et odio, voluptatem amet eius? Alias vitae eveniet ipsum architecto numquam reprehenderit sed exercitationem quasi!
